lead_paragraph: BEIRUT, Lebanon, April 1 -- No drastic change in the status of Syria and Lebanon may be expected before France's own fate is clarified, it is said in reply to Syrian Nationalist pressure.
abstract: Vichy unable to cope with Syrian situation
